name: Ticket info for HammerJacK at GLive, Guildford, Nov 8th
description:
HammerJacK have been invited to play the 1000+ capacity GLive venue in Guildford on Fri 8th November!!

This is going to be a charity event raising money for the MS Society. It is kinda like an allday music festival with loads of bands and merch/craft/art stalls.

We shall be playing along side some awesome local bands including the fab Nylon Sky, Echo Park, Red Kites plus more to be confirmed!

More details and ticket info here: 

http://www.mssociety.org.uk/ms-events/2013/08/guildford-alternative-music-showcase 

HJ x
